data.description: Nestled within the tranquil confines of Langston Ridge West subdivision, this charming ranch-style home offers the perfect blend of comfort and serenity. As you step inside, you're greeted by an open and inviting living space, where the living room seamlessly transitions into the dining room and kitchen, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and ample counter space for culinary adventures. The thoughtful floor plan places the primary bedroom on one side of the house, offering privacy and tranquility. Step outside to discover the large covered porch, overlooking the expansive backyard. On nearly half an acre in size, lush greenery and towering trees provide a picturesque backdrop for outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own slice of paradise. Schedule your showing today and experience the beauty and comfort of Langston Ridge West living!
